description: Ophthalmologists looking for a little help will find that the Ophthalmic Assistant will aid in uncovering research articles easily just by asking. The Ophthalmic Assistant finds relevant articles from trusted sources such as the American Academy of Ophthalmology. New articles are added frequency.
exampleInteractions: Alexa, ask my ophthalmic assistant to tell me about laser scanning
Alexa, ask my ophthalmic assistant to find me an article about corneal ulcers
name: Ophthalmic Assistant
shortDescription: The Ophthalmic Assistant finds articles assist in research and understanding for ophthalmologists.
